casebody.data:
The State ex rel. Peeples, Appellant, v. Wilford, Appellee.

[Cite as State ex rel. Peeples v. Wilford (1995), 72 Ohio St.3d 407.]

(No. 95-276 Submitted April 18, 1995 Decided June 28, 1995.) *408 Kavin Lee Peeples, pro se. Per Curiam.

We affirm the decision of the court of appeals for the reasons stated in its judgment entry.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
